Name: Wo kommst du her?
Notes: Unveröffentlichte Lieder von Fanny Hensel in einem neuen Sammelband. A new collection with songs by Fanny Hensel which are all first publications.
Long Description: A collection of selected songs for soprano and piano, including 'Wo kommst du her?' by Heinrich Wilhelm von Gerstenberg, among others. This is a new collection featuring unpublished songs by Fanny Hensel, all of which are first publications.
Short Description: Selected songs for soprano and piano by Fanny Hensel, including 'Wo kommst du her?'
